  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ako imate vise uslova koje treba obraditi, mozete povezati <code>if</code> iskaze sa <code>else if</code> iskazima.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">if (num > 15) {\n  return \"Bigger than 15\";\n} else if (num &#x3C; 5) {\n  return \"Smaller than 5\";\n} else {\n  return \"Between 5 and 15\";\n}\n</code></pre>\n</section>",
  "instructions": "<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Izmenite logiku tako da koristi <code>else if</code> iskaze.</p>\n</section>",
